                                                <h2 class="title-h2">Characteristics of English Betting Sites</h2>
                      
                    </div>

                  
                                        <div class="align-left block-1-1-4 block-count-6 block-type-text">

                                                <div class="paragraph">
    <p>Due to their linguistic predominance, English bookmakers are able to provide a well-rounded offer that aims to satisfy any type of player, from the most experienced and seasoned to the neophyte who plays the occasional top game of the weekend. </p><p>Not only that, but the English betting sites have now expanded so much that they have become familiar to everyone, so much so that it is sometimes difficult to realize that a given platform is stationed across the Channel and not right here in Italy, near us.</p><p>In addition, thanks to their reliability, these betting sites without limits really allow everyone to enjoy a full gaming experience as well as fully protected, thanks to a strict regulation to protect the player. Online gambling throughout the United Kingdom is regulated by the UK Gambling Commission, and is governed by the Gambling Act 2005.</p>  </div>
                      
                    </div>

                  
                                        <div class="align-center--md block-1-1-5 block-count-6 block-type-heading">

                                                <h2 class="title-h2">What are the pros of a UK betting site ?</h2>
                      
                    </div>

                  
                                        <div class="align-left block-1-1-6 block-count-6 block-type-text">

                                                <div class="paragraph">
    <p>More and more players are choosing to rely on no-limit betting sites, mainly due to the key features that confirm their reliability as well as the very high level of the gaming experience.</p><p>Although the different sites have their own characteristics, there are some that are really valid for everyone, and represent now the standard to follow, demonstrating the high level of experience offered to bettors:</p><ul><li><p>reliability and security</p></li><li><p>fast and always available customer support</p></li><li><p>wide range of sporting events</p></li><li><p>Always up-to-date payment methods</p></li><li><p>no limits for bets and payments</p></li><li><p>Welcome bonuses and convenient promotions</p></li></ul><p>To operate in our country, a betting site needs a license. This permission can be granted directly by the Agency of Customs and Monopolies, or by an international body that issues licenses considered valid, of course, in Europe and, specifically, in Italy. Thanks to this strict regulation, any player approaching one of the various no-limit betting sites can be sure to find himself in a reliable environment, where not only his money, but also his personal data are kept safe and in compliance with the rules.</p><p>In addition to this, each site will have a specific section where it will be possible for any user to track which license the platform possesses, along with an identification number.</p><p>Any good sports betting platform must provide its players with a complete experience in all respects. This also includes the customer support section.</p><p>Since these sites operate purely, if not exclusively, online, it is very important that the registered user can ask for help with a problem and receive assistance as quickly as possible. It is the norm for limitless betting sites to offer different ways to their players: <strong>live chat, email address, online form, phone number.</strong></p><p>The most immediate method is definitely the live chat: by entering your email, you can start chatting in real time with the assistance, receiving help in an instant and precise way for your problem. Usually, these chats are active 24 hours a day, 7 days a week. Not all sites offer this service in Italian, so you have to get by in English.</p><p>More and more sites offer different email addresses to contact according to the problem encountered (sending documents, problems with payments, with the account, etc.), with the response time always short, but may vary depending on the request. This same type of contact we find in the online form: you must fill out a form for reporting, with everything that will then be managed by email.</p><p>The main difference is that, in the form, it's usually possible to choose some predefined fields according to the information you want to receive (for example, if you have problems with payments, you can select the object "problems with payments", in order to simplify the request and shorten the time).</p><p>Finally, we have the good old telephone number. More and more platforms manage to offer telephone assistance in Italian, even though the numbers to be contacted are based abroad. This method is definitely one of the favorites, but unfortunately it is customary that the switchboards are only available on weekdays.</p><p>Thanks to an ever-expanding world of sports, no-limit betting sites really do offer a huge amount not only of disciplines to bet on, but also of individual sporting events: starting with soccer and basketball, moving on to lesser known sports such as cricket and table tennis, until you get to the new categories of eSports and virtual sports.</p><p>Deposit and withdrawal methods are also numerous and always up to date, in order to offer players different choices regarding payment methods. They range from bank transfer to Visa and Mastercard, passing through more modern but equally reliable methods, such as Neteller, PaysafeCard, PayPal, Skrill and so on.</p>  </div>
                      
